article_title: Leslie Dach Lays Out Health Care’s Next Phase
article_text:
Leslie Dach, a former Wal-Mart Stores Inc. executive, has been a senior counselor to Health and Human Services Secretary Sylvia Mathews Burwell for more than a year.

With the Affordable Care Act’s third open-enrollment season under way, Mr. Dach sat down with Wall Street Journal Assistant Managing Editor Laura Landro to discuss how...

twitter.description: Health and Human Services counselor, speaking at The Wall Street Journal’s CEO Council conference, discusses the move away from fee-for-service medicine toward a focus on quality.
